LXT2 file dump working is fine.:)<br>
But I can't found the way for GTKWave simultaneously wave dumping solution with LXT2.<br>
In the VCD dumping, that's the way to overriding a solution with the VerilatedVcdFile base class.<br>
But not LXT2 for me yet...<br>

```
class VerilatedVcdGTKWave : public VerilatedVcdFile
{
public:
	VerilatedVcdGTKWave();
	virtual ~VerilatedVcdGTKWave();

	virtual bool open(const std::string& name);
	virtual void close();
	virtual ssize_t write(const char* buf, ssize_t len);

	.......
};

```
<br>
And I can applying the overriding waveform dump class as the below.<br>
```
g_pGtkWave	= new VerilatedVcdGTKWave;
g_pWaveDump	= new VerilatedVcdC(g_pGtkWave);

```
Is there just possible this way with VCD solution?

